Defendant in custody.
Count 1 - possess heroin - NO CONTEST plea.  Convicted.
Sentence Withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for eighteen (18) months, consecutive to the prison sentence presently being served in 13 CF 33 to commence upon defendants discharge date after extended supervision ends.
Conditions of probation:
1) Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
2) Pay court costs;
3) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
4) Submit to random urine screens and pay for same;
5) Maintain absolute sobriety;
6) Provide DNA sample.
Minutes.
